士认为，正是满天飞的假货击垮了这个曾经风光的「冠军」。 如今，百年品牌 100 亿元卖身，令人唏嘘。而这一次出手的，正是擅长抄底的 ABG。 热搜！100 亿元卖了，百年历史知名品牌被「抄底」，三里屯店已关！顶流明星代言，国内风靡一时！为何突然不火了？ | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2870131950619a22d06852213173f8c3_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658556891"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9Lq45qXWyZFDEAMaCTEwODYyNDEwMSDvxZqzBjAAOD5AEHIJNjU4NTU2ODkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1718118540.310175", "card_id": "Q_393114442", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 67}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "星链系统到底强不强？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "不懂，所以想弄明白。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a05c01bf7f2e726750b63252f6520908_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/393114442"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9Lq45qXWyZFDEAMaCDQ5NjM3NDQ3IJe0zPUFMAA4jgFAEXIJMzkzMTE0NDQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1718118540.310459", "card_id": "Q_656087059", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "户外登山有哪些必备的硬核防晒好物？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-07301ec6af63b31a124997a729d643a7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/656087059"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I9Lq45qXWyZFDEAMaCTEwODA3NDkxNiDn9pGyBjAAOC5AEnIJNjU2MDg3MDU5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1718